FAQ

Common
questions.

Still have questions?
team@koreainsider.kr

What can the AI Camera actually do?
The AI Camera handles four categories: Food (menu translation, vegan/halal/allergy info), Documents (labour contracts, visa forms), Life (Ttareungi bikes, T-money cards, signs), and General (auto-detect anything). Results are for reference — always verify safety-critical information independently.
How does multilingual translation work in the community?
Posts are automatically translated so you can write in your native language and other users read in theirs. No manual translation needed — just communicate naturally.
How is the Kuration content personalised?
Our AI system learns your preferences — food interests, travel style, where you're going — and surfaces the most relevant guides from our curated content library. The more you use KOIN, the better it gets.
How is my personal data handled?
Privacy-first by design. We collect only what's necessary, never sell your data, and comply strictly with Korean privacy regulations. Full details in our Privacy Policy.
Which login methods are supported?
Kakao, Google, or Email — choose whichever is most convenient for you.
How can I contact or partner with KOIN?
For press, partnerships, or general enquiries, reach us at team@koreainsider.kr.
